
Setup istio with Demo profile and Grafana and Prometheus will be enabled.

Istio creates few dashboards by connecting to Prometheous


Few additional graphs which could be useful to create and show in Grafana

container_memory_cache{instance="kworker2",pod=~"rating.*"}
container_memory_usage_bytes{instance="kworker2",pod=~"rating.*"}
container_processes{instance="kworker2"}
grpc_server_msg_received_total
